                <h1>Duke men&#039;s lacrosse takes down No. 16 Richmond </h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/f24d92bb-4ab1-4324-934a-84a56e194310.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Nakeie&#x20;Montgomery&#x20;was&#x20;a&#x20;key&#x20;contributor&#x20;Friday.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Nakeie Montgomery was a key contributor Friday.</p>

